   Institute of Agricultural Research-INIA Uruguay) and Ruth Scholz for
   assistance with field and greenhouse phenotyping. This research was
   supported by the INNOVAGRO program of the National Agency of Research
   and Innovation of Uruguay (ANII), through Grant PR-FSA-2009-1-1369.
