   [Sharma, T. R.; Singh, N. K.] Natl Res Ctr Plant Biotechnol, New Delhi 110012, India.
   [Rathour, Rajeev] CSKHPKV, ACHBB, Palampur 176062, Himachal Prades, India.
   [Variar, Mukund] CRRI, Cent Rainfed Upland Rice Res Stn, Hazaribagh 825301, Jharkhand, India.
