   99/2012]
FX The present work was funded through the UEFISCDI ANCS (National
   Authority for Scientific Research) Research Project PCCA 99/2012
   "Phenotypic and molecular approaches to develop durable adult plant
   (slow-rusting, race non-specific) resistance to leaf rust (Puccinia
   triticina) in wheat (Triticum aestivum)".
