   [Carver, Brett F.] Oklahoma State Univ, Plant & Soil Sci Dept, Stillwater, OK 74075 USA.
   [Zhan, Kehui] Henan Agr Univ, Dept Agron, Zhengzou 450002, Peoples R China.
