   [James, A. T.] Univ Queensland, CSIRO Agr Flagship, Queensland Biosci Precinct, St Lucia, Qld 4072, Australia.
   [Lawn, R. J.] James Cook Univ, Trop Crop Sci Unit, Townsville, Qld 4811, Australia.
   [Lawn, R. J.] James Cook Univ, CSIRO Agr Flagship, ATSIP, Townsville, Qld 4811, Australia.
