   Natural Science, China (Project 2007 GQN0197), and partly by Centre for
   Crop Systems Analysis, Wageningen University, Netherlands. G. A. K.
   acknowledges the Netherlands Fellowship Programme for the financial
   grant of an MSc scholarship.
