   Eulgem (both University of California, Riverside) for comments on the
   manuscript; G. Walker, C. Weirauch, L. Walling, J. Ng, and H. Jin (all
   University of California, Riverside) for discussions; and Cyril Zipfel
   (The Sainsbury Laboratory) for Arabdopsis bak1-5 mutant. This work was
