   [Qin, Lin; Ma, Zhengqiang] Nanjing Agr Univ, Key Lab Crop Genet & Germplasm Enhancement, Nanjing 210095, Jiangsu, Peoples R China.
RP Zhang, XY (reprint author), Chinese Acad Agr Sci, Inst Crop Sci, Key Lab Crop Gene Resources & Germplasm Enhancme, Minist Agr,Natl Key Facil Crop Gene Resources & G, Beijing 100081, Peoples R China.
