   [Du Cheyron, Philippe; Daucourt, Joelle] Univ Paris 11, IBP, Arvalis Inst Vegetal, F-91405 Orsay, France.
   [Lorgeou, Josiane; Piraux, Francis] Arvalis Inst Vegetal, Stn Expt, F-91720 Boigneville, France.
