   [Christensen, Kris A.; Brunelli, Joseph P.; Lambert, Matthew J.; DeKoning, Jenefer; Phillips, Ruth B.; Thorgaard, Gary H.] Washington State Univ, Ctr Reprod Biol, Pullman, WA 99164 USA.
RP Christensen, KA (reprint author), Washington State Univ, Sch Mol Biosci, Pullman, WA 99164 USA.
