   Engineering Research Council of Canada Discovery Grant Program for this
   research. We also express our sincere thanks to Harry Muc (Department of
   Animal Science, University of Manitoba) for his technical assistance and
   animal care, and Granny's Hatchery Division, Granny's Poultry
   Co-operative (Manitoba) Ltd for free day-old chicks used in the current
   study.
