   [O'Shea, Charlotte; Lindemose, Soren; Skriver, Karen] Univ Copenhagen, Dept Biol, Ole Maaloes Vej 5, Copenhagen N, Denmark.
   [Mollegaard, Niels Erik] Univ Copenhagen, Dept Cellular & Mol Med, Blegdamsvej 3B, Copenhagen N, Denmark.
