   [Hanzalova, Alena] Crop Res Inst, Dept Genet & Plant Breeding Methods, Drnovska 507-73, CZ-16106 Prague 6, Czech Republic.
   [Horcicka, Pavel] Selgen AS, Breeding Stn Stupice, Stupice 24, Sibrina 25084, Czech Republic.
