   [Kettlewell, P. S.] Harper Adams Univ, Newport, Shrops, England.
   [Simmonds, J.; Flintham, J. E.; Snape, J. W.] John Innes Ctr, Dept Crop Genet, Norwich, Norfolk, England.
   [Werner, P.] KWS Ltd, Thriplow, Herts, England.
