OI Semagn, Kassa/0000-0001-6486-5685
FU Bill & Melinda Gates Foundation; Howard Buffet Foundation
FX We are grateful to J. Crossa for the initial phenotype data analyses,
   CIMMYT Field Technicians at the different stations in Kenya, Zimbabwe
   and Zambia for the phenotypic evaluation, and the Monsanto Company for
   genotyping the populations and also providing marker database that links
   the genetic positions of the proprietary SNP markers with public
   markers. This work was carried as part of the WEMA project that has been
