   [Li, Jiarui] Kansas State Univ, Dep Plant Pathol, Manhattan, KS 66506 USA.
   [Tang, Yimiao] Beijing Acad Agr & Forestry Sci, Beijing Hybrid Wheat Res Ctr, Beijing 100089, Peoples R China.
