   [Jia, Jizeng] Chinese Acad Agr Sci, Key Lab Crop Germplasm Resources & Utilizat, Natl Key Facil Crop Gene Resources & Genet Improv, Minist Agr,Inst Crop Sci, Beijing 100081, Peoples R China.
