FU 111 Project from the Education Ministry of China [B07049]; National 11th
   Five-Year Plan Key Project, China [2006BAD08A05]; Toxicity Variation of
   Wheat Stripe Rust Pathogen and Demonstration of Integrated Management of
   Stripe Rust, China [200903035-02]
