   Ressources Genetique, France. It was part of the project 'Etude des
   complementarites entre modes de gestion dynamique (a la ferme ou en
   station) et statique a partir du cas du ble tendre. The authors thank
   farmers from the Reseau Semences Paysannes and Jean Koening, the
   genebank curator who provided seed samples for the study and for their
