   [Tsilo, Toi] Small Grain Inst, Agr Res Council, Bethlehem, South Africa.
   [Rouse, Matthew N.; Jin, Yue] Univ Minnesota, USDA ARS, Cereal Dis Lab, St Paul, MN 55108 USA.
